1
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,959
Do you believe me now?

2
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:32,120
I should've perished a millennium ago.

3
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,640
Yet you've kept my belongings

4
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,879
all this time,

5
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:44,920
and now I've found a new vessel.

6
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,680
Jiang Yue.

7
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,640
Her memories are fragmented.

8
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,480
From now on, I'll take her place.

9
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,920
Is that alright?

10
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,400
You are?

11
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,639
Ms. Li.

12
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,680
Sir,

13
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,000
you are old.

14
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,680
Just call me Fei.

15
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,960
Fei?

16
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,599
How dare you!

17
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,680
Miss,

18
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,759
whether you are Jiang Yue or Li Feiyuan,

19
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:22,840
you should know

20
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,840
that if you hurt our leader,

21
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,719
we won't let you go.

22
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,039
I didn't hurt him.

23
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,199
He disobeyed my order,

24
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,800
so he deserves

25
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,520
the pain of being burnt by fire,

26
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,759
and the pain of being bitten by ants.

27
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:40,560
What do you want me to do?

28
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,120
I just said

29
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,560
I want to live here

30
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:47,960
and let you serve me.

31
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,080
This is the most delicious food

32
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,360
in your time.

33
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,680
It's pancake.

34
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,680
Pizza.

35
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:12,680
Li Si bought them.

36
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,120
What a strange Chinese medicine.

37
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,240
It tastes good.

38
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,680
This is cola.

39
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,199
Li Si bought it.

40
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,000
The flower arrangement you asked me to prepare,

41
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,719
and the incense,

42
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,199
are all ready.

43
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,439
They're arranged in the room.

44
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,280
This is not the Li residence.

45
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,840
That means,

46
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,680
if you want to go back to your hometown,

47
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,680
you can take a plane.

48
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,080
How can a chicken take a plane?

49
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,400
By car is also fine.

50
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,800
A car with four wheels,

51
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,039
no need for horse power,

52
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,000
and faster speed.

53
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,479
Let's go.

54
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,199
Take me to see it.

55
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,680
Where are we going?

56
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,160
Take me to drink.

57
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,120
This tavern is so dark,

58
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,439
not even the lanterns are lit.

59
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,199
Sir, Madam,

60
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:46,959
what would you like to drink?

61
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,240
A coke.

62
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,519
I've had coke before.

63
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,519
Something else.

64
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,319
What's this?

65
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,639
What is this?

66
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,000
Order everything on this.

67
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:06,959
Sir,

68
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,399
is that okay?

69
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,480
Go ahead.

70
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:14,360
Okay.

71
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:25,519
Waiter,

72
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,120
ten more.

73
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,759
You will get drunk.

74
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,399
I'm not drunk yet.

75
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,680
You are a good drinker.

76
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,800
This wine tastes good,

77
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,160
but it's a little weak.

78
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:44,839
I can drink thousands of cups.

79
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,800
You are so arrogant.

80
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,120
Let's have a competition.

81
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,759
What do you mean?

82
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,279
When you are in the world,

83
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:57,600
you must be hurt.

84
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,000
Five times, you will die. Three times, you will die.

85
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,480
I'll kill you with one.

86
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,160
Go!

87
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,160
Ready.

88
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,399
Go!

89
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,079
Come on!

90
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:11,360
Go, go, go!

91
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:14,360
Come on, come on, come on!

92
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:25,519
Go get the wine.

93
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,079
Let's go home.

94
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,160
Go get the wine.

95
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,720
Hidden Edge.

96
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,879
Go get the wine.

97
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,480
Go!

98
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,720
Do you have any other games?

99
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:40,879
Teach me.

100
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,439
You saw it.

101
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,120
The biggest mistake a hunter makes

102
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,000
is being kind to the prey.

103
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,439
I should have killed her.

104
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,160
Then you wouldn't be like this,

105
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,160
with no dignity.

106
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,000
Li Feiyuan is dead.

107
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,839
Are you telling me

108
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,839
you trained her to be like Li Feiyuan?

109
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,759
You like being a dog, don't you?

110
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,399
I'll beat you if you keep talking nonsense.

111
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,240
Go ahead.

112
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,839
That's Jiang Yue's body,

113
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,360
just controlled by Li Feiyuan's consciousness.

114
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:41,240
What's the difference?

115
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,040
Just kill her.

116
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,920
Even if you remember the old days

117
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:48,279
and put down your own grudges,

118
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:52,120
you can't forget our parents' grudges.

119
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,480
I haven't forgotten.

120
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:54,639
That's good.

121
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,000
This sword

122
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,319
was used to skin our parents.

123
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,199
You can use it to avenge them.

124
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,680
Perfect.

125
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,079
Zang Feng,

126
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,759
let's go home.

127
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,399
[Where am I?]

128
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,159
[Li Feiyuan,]

129
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:12,000
[did she trap me here?]

130
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,360
Send me the location.

131
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,000
It's my first time meeting Mr Xie.

132
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,759
You look and act

133
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,440
remind me of your father

134
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,600
in his younger days.

135
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:54,720
You've met my father?

136
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,519
We've been business partners

137
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,799
since 16 years ago.

138
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,480
Mr Xie built a world-renowned

139
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:03,399
biopharmaceutical group from scratch,

140
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,399
yet he retired early.

141
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:08,480
It seems he has high hopes for you.

142
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,759
No need for pleasantries.

143
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:13,080
If you can't get this shipment out,

144
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,039
my father will be disappointed

145
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,360
in me and you.

146
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,240
There's a local bully on the island

147
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:20,480
occupying the port and acting tyrannically.

148
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,679
He forbids our cargo ships to pass.

149
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,879
You're the boss of such a big gang,

150
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:27,399
and you still have something to fear?

151
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:30,000
The leader is Lu Zhiyu,

152
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,879
who is even more wicked,

153
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:35,039
specializing in luring naive young girls.

154
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,480
The one in his hands now is the most pitiful.

155
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,200
Her name seems to be...

156
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:42,000
Jiang Yue.

157
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,840
Tell me,

158
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,000
where's that Lu guy?

159
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,240
Get some rest.

160
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,840
You're leaving?

161
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,320
I'm a man.

162
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,679
It's inappropriate to share a room with a woman.

163
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:10,799
In the tavern, so many men

164
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:15,039
kept drinking and playing games with me.

165
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,879
Only you, Zang Feng,

166
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,200
were as cold as ice to me.

167
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,320
It's really quite boring.

168
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,559
They have ulterior motives.

169
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,639
You don't understand this era.

170
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,639
And you?

171
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,480
What are your intentions?

172
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,039
I've been loyal to my master,

173
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,919
never overstepping boundaries.

174
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,559
On our wedding night,

175
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,559
you took me from the Liu Mansion.

176
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,200
You overstepped boundaries quite a bit.

177
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:13,240
The Liu family is infamous.

178
00:12:15,679 --> 00:12:17,080
I was loyal to my master,

179
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,879
unable to bear seeing him suffer.

180
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,919
I was foolish

181
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,440
to have never believed

182
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,720
the Lis bore a blood feud with my parents.

183
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,879
You too

184
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,720
are a cruel person.

185
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:50,200
Then kill me

186
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,639
and avenge your family.

187
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,080
What?

188
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,879
Do you feel sorry for me

189
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,360
or for

190
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,840
this borrowed body?

191
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,120
I love this era.

192
00:13:40,639 --> 00:13:42,879
No need to follow those admonishments

193
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:44,559
or rules.

194
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,639
We can go anywhere we want.

195
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,799
From now on,

196
00:13:53,639 --> 00:13:54,799
I'll be by your side.

197
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,080
Is that okay?

198
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,159
If you come back,

199
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,440
what about Jiang Yue?

200
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,120
She'll be in the abyss

201
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:08,799
or

202
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,440
her soul will be scattered.

203
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:19,559
I've always wanted to see you again

204
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,559
and ask you why you abandoned me.

205
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:28,919
[But that would be]

206
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,399
[unfair to Jiang Yue.]

207
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,039
Jiang Yue?

208
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,320
Lu Zhiyu?
